title: Pumpkin and ginger loaf cake
ingredients: ['600g sugar', '250ml vegetable oil', '4 eggs', '150ml water', '425g pumpkin puree', '2 teaspoons ground ginger', '1 teaspoon ground allspice', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1 teaspoon ground cloves', '440g plain flour', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1 1/2 teaspoons salt', '1/2 teaspoon baking powder']
